        <h2>ERASMUS+</h2>
        <p>
            Erasmus+ is the new EU programme for Education, Training, Youth and Sport for 2014-2020, starting in January 2014, which aims at boosting skills and employability, and modernising Education, Training and Youth work.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://ec.europa.eu/programmes/erasmus-plus/index_en.htm">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
