    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Youth on the Move</h2>
        <p>Youth on the Move was launched in 2010 as a part of the Europe 2020 Strategy for growth and employment, and it consists of a package of policy initiatives that aim to improve young people’s education and employability, to reduce high youth unemployment and to increase the youth-employment rate</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://ec.europa.eu/youthonthemove/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
