        <p>The main reason is to pursue their studies, but the sunny climate, the language or the opportunity to experience life in a different country are also factors that prove attractive to the many foreigners enrolling in Portuguese universities.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.portugaldailyview.com/whats-new/erasmus-a-guide-to-studying-in-portugal">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
